Package: @CODENAME_SAFE@-nox-settings
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         @CODENAME_SAFE@-common-settings
Description: provide default noX settings (installed mode)
 Provides default settings for appearance and applications of noX
 in siduction.
 .
 This overrides nox's defaults used for new users, all settings remain
 configurable by the local user and don't override already existing user
 profiles.

